ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔知點面對佢"},{"pid":"f7648837b098964ca3a10f2454cf4eba4ed8e9c5","tid":160941,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪搵水泡咋？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能啦<br />\n其實我都心郁郁<br />\n不過會好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6603ed8c7731de6bbef5bd91a9ff0d11a3833cf","tid":160941,"uid":27289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"呢d女最麻撚煩<br />\n做Sp都免"},{"pid":"4bb1f92864840697a2555faf4edb1287940b6de4","tid":160941,"uid":44179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:09:50.000Z","msg":"中出即飛"},{"pid":"0cfa19f5e98b0cb5d5555f58f604ec954fc71d57","tid":160941,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:11:00.000Z","msg":"你女朋友真係慘"},{"pid":"c3933eb6b9186482d230ffd0e7a8f8a5f6d84f17","tid":160941,"uid":88230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:11:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6564975857ab1c1624c01da1349903115aa7319","tid":160941,"uid":22175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:11:18.000Z","msg":"有得食唔真係唔食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a29d9943a59facd4f11ee85e4357b6250391c35","tid":160941,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"有得屌未食住先囉"},{"pid":"259476c1c70640ec891240e8eee552b76affedc2","tid":160941,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:14:28.000Z","msg":"你係唔係扑過人阿？"},{"pid":"fb77453bcd29c997838e9c76f3a7e89d94b8538d","tid":160941,"uid":14961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:19:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中</span></span>"},{"pid":"ccb0e44fa0d1fef20b926b6ad2c4221fc882793e","tid":160941,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:24:12.000Z","msg":"你女朋友真係慘"},{"pid":"b623fc8bacdb30fcea9a390cbbebf91146d82a25","tid":160941,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"跳船正食屎狗"},{"pid":"4b4cb7edfc6313795522cfc7c728d9de9026f382","tid":160941,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:28:58.000Z","msg":"留名是俾高質故的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8926921009694dac87a2e8175aa90d9dff1dd882","tid":160941,"uid":9098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同事玩過就算<br />\n唔好認真<br />\n見到多係會日久生情<br />\n同你中學/大學溝女既道理冇乜大分別</blockquote><br />\n唔好貪一時犯規既快感，<br />\n而無咗一個真心為你付出既女朋友；<br />\n<br />\n你係想食既，確保無手尾至好，<br />\n有一絲唔確定既，你都係做返專一男啦"},{"pid":"b8d5a40d4d020c08f434581fd8020a4ea317d7d2","tid":160941,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係唔係扑過人阿？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇呀<br />\n正常同事開係"},{"pid":"17ba902095c1c4af4c783e9cad82851d167785fd","tid":160941,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:35:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同事玩過就算<br />\n唔好認真<br />\n見到多係會日久生情<br />\n同你中學/大學溝女既道理冇乜大分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都明 但係以後應該點面對佢好 我又唔捨得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d853078d702d9b9b2a9587b6b074ab9c81acc3","tid":160941,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:38:17.000Z","msg":"日見日見 日久生情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb99941ed13fa2b7b5e8e2609f46fa0430561003","tid":160941,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"大波但靚唔靚先"},{"pid":"f178290ebc870e1b72a29714f2395f4b013e0ba6","tid":160941,"uid":32570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:3